TITLE: Initializing DataTables with jQuery
DESCRIPTION: Basic initialization of DataTables on an HTML table using jQuery. This simple example applies the default DataTables enhancements to any selected table element.
SOURCE: https://github.com/datatables/datatables/blob/master/Readme.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
$('table').dataTable();
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Configuring DataTables with Options
DESCRIPTION: Advanced initialization of DataTables using configuration options. This example disables pagination and enables vertical scrolling with a height of 300 pixels.
SOURCE: https://github.com/datatables/datatables/blob/master/Readme.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
$('table').dataTable( {
  paginate: false,
  scrollY: 300
} );
```

