DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet showcases the data structure for populating a DataTable. It contains employee records with fields for name, position, office location, ID number, start date, and salary, formatted as a nested array where each inner array represents a row of data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/datatables/datatables/blob/master/examples/ajax/data/arrays_custom_prop.txt#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    [
        [
            "Donna Snider",
            "Customer Support",
            "New York",
            "4226",
            "2011\/01\/25",
            "$112,000"
        ]
    ]
}
```

